    key: "litTermsofUseSubText3",
    scope: "",
    en:
      "If you use the Site, you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password, as well as for restricting access to your computer, and you agree to accept responsibility for all activities that occur under your account or password. You are 18 years of age or older. Social Systems Evidence and its partners, attorneys, staff and affiliates (collectively, 'Affiliated Parties') reserve the right to refuse service, terminate accounts, remove or edit content, or cancel orders in their sole discretion.",
