    en:
      "<p>\n\nThe translations of <b>Social Systems Evidence</b> into languages other than English and French are made possible by a<br />collaboration between the \n\n<a href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=McMaster Health Forum&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.mcmasterhealthforum.org%2f'>\n\nMcMaster Health Forum\n\n</a> \n\nand five additional partners:\n\n<br /></p><p><a href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=WHO Regional Office for the Eastern Mediterranean&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.emro.who.int%2findex.asp' target='_blank'>\n\nWHO Regional Office for the Eastern Mediterranean \n\n</a> \n\nand the \n\n<a href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=American University of Beirut&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.aub.edu.lb%2f' target='_blank'>\n\n American University of Beirut\n\n</a> \n\n(for Arabic) \n</p><p> <a href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=EBMC Lanzhou U&L=http%3a%2f%2febm.lzu.edu.cn%2f' target='_blank'>\n\nEvidence-Based Medicine Center\n\n</a>, \n\nLanzhou University (for Chinese)<br />\n\n</p><p> <a href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=Pan Am Health Org&L=http%3a%2f%2fnew.paho.org%2f' target='_blank'>\n\nPan American Health Organization\n\n</a> \n\n(for Portuguese and Spanish) \n\n</p><p> <a href='R.aspx?U=[USERID]&T=EXTERNAL&D=WHO Regional Office for Europe&L=http%3a%2f%2fwww.euro.who.int%2fen%2fhome' target='_blank'>\n\nWHO Regional Office for Europe\n\n</a> \n\n(for Russian)\n\n</p><p><img src='images/Translators.gif' alt='Translator Logos' usemap='#translator_map' /></p>",
